DNS Client API

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
                   THIS API IS STILL WORK IN PROGRESS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

The DNS Client API for Zephyr is a collection of C files:

    - dns_pack.h, dns_pack.c:
        RFC 1035 serialization and deserialization functions

    - dns_utils.h. dns_utils.c:
	Helper functions

